data.title: Manitoba Moon Sat Sep 23 with David on CKUW FM Winnipeg
data.meta_description: This is a music based show highlighting an eclectic mix of genres from my extensive collection. I intend to keep things weird, wild and science fictitious traversing topics including but not limited to space travel, monsters and mayhem, and space invasion. The flow will have lycanthropic changes enticing you to stay tuned through the wee hours.Manitoba Moon broadcasts every Saturday from 12:00am – 6:00am (CT)
